Startup globals and bootstrapping are represented by importer initialization plus server startup checks.
Legacy file-combine report generation maps to modern report/case-packet export logic and template rendering.
Adobe/report-combine variants are covered by modern markdown/PDF pipeline and export parity validation.
Error handling is mapped to API/runtime exception handling and strict parity gate failures.
Core MVQS calculations are represented in modern computation and report assembly endpoints.
Legacy open-file actions map to modern case/report export and retrieval endpoints.
